 the different realms, bouncing off the walls, wrapping enemies in bubbles and leaving everything in your path squeaky clean. Antique civilizations await in your journey, as you meet charming characters to befriend and, most importantly, try to restore the order.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295430/extras/f7a63c89ebda9e237ea3f4f90ca92180.poster.avif?t=1765355424\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295430/extras/f7a63c89ebda9e237ea3f4f90ca92180.webm?t=1765355424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295430/extras/f7a63c89ebda9e237ea3f4f90ca92180.mp4?t=1765355424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295430/extras/501a209070747c5e6e37d791243da777.webp?t=1765355424\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295430/extras/101cc8c2a7b07e016dccee637b0cafc4.poster.avif?t=1765355424\" width=600 height=30 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295430/extras/101cc8c2a7b07e016dccee637b0cafc4.webm?t=1765355424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Dungeon Cleaner</strong> is a Roguelite with never-before-seen mechanics.<br>He plays the charismatic &quot;Bubble Guy&quot;, inhabitant of a world terraformed by gods after a great war.<br><br>Instead of using weapons, the Bubble Guy will bounce off the walls of the changing and mysterious dungeons while trapping enemies that cross his descent in bubbles! <br><br><span class=\"bb_im